      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "BRIAN (1) was on speed settling but found some traffic when checked, missing the frame to finish fifth (18.10) at this track in a Grade 6/MDN. Should be in this for a long way. MOONLIGHT HAZE (2) racing well without winning, placing at his last four runs. Last time finished 2nd in a Maiden on May 31 over 305m at this track behind Inga Noah beaten a nose (17.98). Expecting another good run. DIVINE POWER (4) is on debut and has a tricky draw to overcome. Expected to play a major role. BOURNE REAGAN (7) is by Mcinerney out of Sweet On Me making debut. Start all important and will need some luck getting across from the wide draw. Can run a bold race on debut.",
